snippet.title: TimeWarp: City Demo
snippet.description:
A new demo for my HL1 mod TimeWarp has been released, containing half of the city chapter and plenty of exciting action!

Jay and Patient 84 head to 2010 in order to find the last Time Crystal, however it won't be that easy as a lot of well-trained, well armed mercenaries were hired to protect it! You and Jay must blast through the city and retrieve the crystal at all costs!

Check out the mod here: https://www.moddb.com/mods/timewarp
and join the Discord server: https://discord.gg/PSSSzmj2JR
